OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain affects northern and
OL,6,Fwestern areas on Tuesday, becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly showery. Some outbreaks
OL,8,Fwill be heavy and possibly thundery in
OL,9,Fthe north. Patchy rain may briefly
OL,10,Faffect southeast England. Elsewhere,
OL,11,Fmostly cloudy with some brighter
OL,12,Fspells. Temperatures close to normal.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers will continue into
OL,15,Fthe evening, some locally heavy, but
OL,16,Fit will become increasingly dry
OL,17,Ftowards midnight, with clear spells
OL,18,Fdeveloping. Cloud will increase across
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
