OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloud and rain across
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland will spread eastwards
OL,7,Finto Scotland during the day, with
OL,8,Fsome heavier bursts possible.
OL,9,FElsewhere, it will be largely dry,
OL,10,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
